  <part>
    <title>Introduction</title>
    <partintro>
      <para>
        This part gives an introduction into the OpenEngSB project and explains it base usage environment
        and the base concepts, such as Tool Domains, Tool Connectors, OpenEngSB workflows and similar
        important ideas.
      </para>
    </partintro>
    <xi:include href="introduction/introduction.xml" />
  </part>

  <part>
    <title>Setup &amp; Administration</title>
    <partintro>
      <para>
        This part explains the usage of the OpenEngSB in a real environment. It explains how to install,
        setup and use the OpenEngSB administration interface to implement a tool environment according
        to your needs.
      </para>
    </partintro>
    <xi:include href="administration/userQuickstart.xml" />
    <xi:include href="administration/testclient.xml" />
  </part>

